<br>
Free Peoples:<br>
 Well, it&#39;s pretty easy. Make sure Boromir gets armor. once he gets the horn, you can afford to start using his game text without feeding them. I usually give Aragorn the Last Alliance first since he is more of a beatdown. I would have put in a couple of Flaming brands but couldnt find room (please give suggestion pls and ty). Once Elrond gets Vilya, he can return any condition to the players hand (might want to save some vitality for healing people in the regroup phase). I like to play Galadriel, the mirror, and Nenya because I like discarding opponents cards and discarding my cards so my hand isnt that clogged. Don&#39;t be afraid to play Elves for the twilight because once Boromir gets the horn, try to swarm them with archery. You may be thinking &quot;Why in the world is this idiot playing Gandalf&#39;s cart, O Elbereth! Githoneol!, and Mithril Coat????&quot; Gandalf&#39;s Cart : Hand unclogger if you have possessions and no owners. O E-something: buh bye Nazguls and +1. Mithril Coat: 1 wound and -1 archery wow isnt taht nice. Well i think thats it for the Free Peoples.<br>
